Class XPathExpressionWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.std.datatypes.XPathExpressionWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.xml.xpath.XPathExpression

    public class XPathExpressionWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.xml.xpath.XPathExpression
    XPathExpressionWrapper implements the XPathExpression interface to wrap another XPathExpression and keep the path expression that was used to create it.
